OL,3,CRestaurant owner blackmailed with bad
OL,4,Creviews warns of scam
OL,6,FThe owner of a restaurant in
OL,7,FWorcestershire is speaking out after
OL,8,Fhe was targeted by an online
OL,9,Fblackmailer.
OL,11,FThe scammer posted negative reviews
OL,12,Fabout Sam Morgan's business after he
OL,13,Frefused to send a large sum of money.
OL,15,FThe reviews have now been removed but
OL,16,FSam is warning other restaurant and
OL,17,Fcafe owners about the scam, which is
OL,18,Fbeing examined by fraud investigators.
