OL,3,CRestaurant owner blackmailed with bad
OL,4,Creviews warns of scam
OL,6,FHe says the demands for money began
OL,7,Fearlier this month, with the person
OL,8,Fthreatening to post highly negative
OL,9,Freviews - unless he sent them the
OL,10,Fmoney.
OL,12,FThe request was first proposed as a
OL,13,Fplea for a loan but soon turned into
OL,14,Fan outright demand for cash.
OL,16,F"The sum of money was #2000 initially,
OL,17,Fthat figure kept changing as the as
OL,18,Ftime passed", explained Sam. "So the
OL,19,Fthreat was that if we don't pay
OL,20,Fimmediately the figure will continue
OL,21,Fto increase."
