OL,3,CRestaurant owner blackmailed with bad
OL,4,Creviews warns of scam
OL,6,FSam, who used to work in law
OL,7,Fenforcement, used a dummy mobile phone
OL,8,Fto pose as 'Louise', the supposed
OL,9,Fowner of the restaurants.
OL,11,FHe exchanged a number of messages over
OL,12,FWhatsapp with the fraudster and -
OL,13,Fafter 'Louise' repeatedly refused to
OL,14,Fpay the money - negative reviews began
OL,15,Fto appear online.
