OL,6,F"What we can see very clearly, what's
OL,7,Fbeen identified, is that they were
OL,8,Fripping the identification of other
OL,9,Fpeople, true people, people that are
OL,10,Fin America, etc. and trying to create
OL,11,Fa profile that looked verified or at
OL,12,Fleast credible in some way."
OL,14,FSam gathered enough evidence to prove
OL,15,Fa link and reported it to all of the
OL,16,Fonline platforms involved.
