OL,3,CRestaurant owner blackmailed with bad
OL,4,Creviews warns of scam
OL,6,FMessages such as "I'll do that until I
OL,7,Fget the loan from you" and "I'll
OL,8,Fmention your name on the reviews" were
OL,9,Fsent to intimidate Sam into handing
OL,10,Fover the money.
OL,12,FThe amount of money in the demand was
OL,13,Fthen increased.
OL,15,FDespite all of this Sam didn't hand
OL,16,Fover any money - but he says that
OL,17,Fother restaurant owners might fall
OL,18,Finto the scammer's trap.
