OL,3,CRestaurant owner blackmailed with bad
OL,4,Creviews warns of scam
OL,6,F"It's a modern-day extortion
OL,7,Fprotection racket. It's effectively
OL,8,Fpay us some money or we're going to
OL,9,Fdestroy your business", said Sam.
OL,10,F"Ultimately, if they can see that
OL,11,Fsomeone like me is quite happy to
OL,12,Fspeak about it publicly then hopefully
OL,13,Fother restaurants can feel secure by
OL,14,Fthat and reach out as well and not
OL,15,Fbeen duped into paying these
OL,16,Forganisations any money."
OL,18,FAll of the evidence collected by Sam
OL,19,Fhas now been passed to Action Fraud
OL,20,Ffor them to investigate.
